<HEADLINE> Worker Jailed for Psychic Calls </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Cheryl Burnham's psychic should have seen it  
coming. 
</P>
<P>
	Ms. Burnham, a clerk at a juvenile facility, got 30 days in jail  
Thursday for ringing up a $120,000 tab on her employer to a psychic 
hotline. 
