<HEADLINE> Aki Berg Returning to Kings </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	INGLEWOOD, Calif. (AP) -- Restricted free-agent defenseman Aki  
Berg is returning to the Los Angeles Kings, having agreed to terms 
of a one-year contract with the NHL team. 
</P>
